text:
Hi, I’m an Expert in Web Scraping and Browser Automation Using Python. I have more than 3 years of experience in several Web Scraping / Data Extraction projects using python frameworks and other tools (Scrappy and Selenium). I can scrape any website e.g. Dynamic (JavaScript \/ Ajax-based) websites, Login Required Sites, and IP Blocking Sites. I can provide Scrapped data in XLSX, CSV (Google Sheets or Excel), JSON, or any other desired database. I have Strong Grip on Python libraries like: - Scrappy, Selenium, Requests, Beautiful Soup, Api etc.
#pythonskillsacademy #webscraping #webautomation
